===============================================================================
README - xcc-ruby
===============================================================================

Run all Unit Tests:

* rake alltests

Build docs:

* rake rdoc

INSTALL

Option 1.

* Download ruby gem: https://code.qnot.org/svn/projects/marklogic/packages/GEMS/

* gem install ruby-xcc

Option 2. 

* rake install

Option 3. 

* ruby extconf.rb --with-mlxcc-dir=/usr/local (libmlxcc path) 

* make

* make install

AUTHOR

